title: Ep - 43 - Real World 25th Anniversary: Norman Korpi & Southern Charm's Catherine Cooper
description:
In celebration of the 25th anniversary of Real World, Kate chats with Norman Korpi from the first season in New York. Catherine Cooper from Southern Charm Savannah calls from an Uber in New York and discusses how life has changed since the show. Buzz Feed’s Senior Entertainment Editor Jarett Wieselman is forced to watch Undercover Boss: Celebrity Edition with Kate and they both shed puddles of tears.
